 midfielder, Camavinga finds the cutting pass to beat the midfield press and launch a counter-attack." data-recalc-dims="1" /> Having cut inside and nutmegged a helpless Lille midfielder, Camavinga finds the cutting pass to beat the midfield press and launch a counter-attack. But with all the technical and dribbling ability, it is nothing without end product. The Frenchman can score and does, on his France debut no less, but his passing is also impressive. Finding cross-field passes which are not simple switches but tactical plays into dangerous positions on the pitch. The key to Camavinga’s game is a consistent want to keep his side on the front foot. <img src="https://i2.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-6-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="Camavinga finds a curling, lofted pass out to the left wing to set up a crossing opportunity." data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i2.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-6-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" class=" jetpack-lazy-image"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=" data-src="https://i2.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-6-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="Camavinga finds a curling, lofted pass out to the left wing to set up a crossing opportunity." data-recalc-dims="1" /><noscript><img src="https://i2.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-6-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="Camavinga finds a curling, lofted pass out to the left wing to set up a crossing opportunity." data-recalc-dims="1" /> Camavinga finds a curling, lofted pass out to the left wing to set up a crossing opportunity. <img src="https://i2.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-6-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt