rned to trust he youngsters ability to find them and consistently he does." data-recalc-dims="1" /><noscript><img src="https://i2.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-5-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="It appears that the Frenchman is able to find passes from almost anywhere on the pitch. His teammates have learned to trust he youngsters ability to find them and consistently he does." data-recalc-dims="1" /> It appears that the Frenchman is able to find passes from almost anywhere on the pitch. His teammates have learned to trust the youngsters ability to find them and consistently he does. Finally, Camavinga’s work ethic is up there with the hardest of working central midfielders. When out of possession the Frenchman craves possession and is always wanting to recover it for his team. Tracking back, spotting opportunities to tackle and typically winning them also, describing him as the complete midfielder is almost an understatement. <img src="https://i1.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-4-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="Camavinga, second to the ball in this scenario, uses his recovery speed to catch the Nice player." data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-4-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" class=" jetpack-lazy-image"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=" data-src="https://i1.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-4-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="Camavinga, second to the ball in this scenario, uses his recovery speed to catch the Nice player." data-recalc-dims="1" /><noscript><img src="https://i1.wp.com/www.101greatgoals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-4-1024x576.png?resize=1024%2C576&#038;ssl=1" alt="Camavinga