6&#038;ssl=1" alt="Winning the ball, fairly, the possession falls back to France. This happening in the 97th minute displays the Frenchman&#039;s commitment and work ethic at any time during the game." data-recalc-dims="1" /> Winning the ball fairly, the possession falls back to France. This happening in the 97th minute displays the Frenchman’s commitment and work ethic at any time during the game. Camavinga is truly a special player. His ceiling is limitless from the evidence displayed during the adolescent years of his career. With his technical skill, body structure, stamina, passing quality and work ethic, these all combine to present a player well beyond his years. Even a role model for players not limited to ages below his own but any player. The story of Camavinga is one the entirety of Europe should take great interest in. View this post on Instagram Le Phantom Secret Tournament commence!  Go voter pour ma team Next Up dans la story @Nikefootball  @deynacastellanos @sandrotonali A post shared by  Eduardo Camavinga (@e.cama10) on Nov 5, 2020 at 5:48am PST Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.